# StampStack project

This repo is **StampStack**, an MV3 Chromium ad blocker (`package.json` name `stampstack-adblock`). The git folder/remote may still be named `quell`.

## Before coding

- Read `AGENTS.md` for commands and hard rules.
- Prefer `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md` when changing SW / DNR / cosmetics flow.

## Do / don't

- **Do** edit `src/` and `scripts/`; regenerate with `npm run build` or `compile-filters`.
- **Don't** hand-edit `src/generated/` or `dist/`.
- **Don't** commit secrets, `node_modules`, or generated artifacts.
- **Do** keep `src/shared/types.ts` message union in sync with all handlers.
- **Do** run `npm run typecheck` after TypeScript changes; after parser/DNR changes also compile filters.

## Commit policy

Only commit when the user explicitly asks.
